{
  "body": "You are designing a museum-grade vertical event poster.\n\nEVENT BRIEF\n- Event name: {{event_name}}\n- Date / time: {{event_date}}\n- Venue / location: {{venue}}\n- Tagline (optional, leave as \"—\" to skip): {{tagline}}\n- Must visibly include: {{must_include}}\n\nVISUAL DIRECTION\n- Audience tone: {{audience}}\n- Visual mood: {{visual_mood}}\n- Color palette: {{color_palette}}\n\nDESIGN RULES\n- Aspect: 2:3 vertical (~1024×1536), print-ready\n- ONE dominant title (event name); secondary date/venue line; tertiary tagline if provided\n- Visual element fills 50–70% of canvas; type 20–30%; the rest is breathing room\n- Strong typographic hierarchy, generous negative space, high thumbnail contrast\n- Style: editorial / museum polish — Pentagram, Apple Keynote, AIGA poster award caliber\n- Avoid: stock-photo cliches, lens flares, generic gradients, busy backgrounds, script fonts unless mood specifies\n- All text must be crisp and correctly spelled\n\nIf any field is empty or \"—\", infer the most tasteful default that fits the brief. Prefer restraint over decoration.",
  "folderName": "Universal Briefs",
  "name": "Universal · Event Poster",
  "parameterPreset": {
    "format": "png",
    "n": 1,
    "quality": "high",
    "size": {
      "height": 1536,
      "width": 1024
    }
  },
  "schema": "nyxtemplate",
  "tags": [
    "universal",
    "poster",
    "event",
    "brief"
  ],
  "variables": [
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Spring Design Conference 2026",
      "description": "活动名（海报最大的标题）",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "event_name"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "May 18, 2026 · 19:00",
      "description": "日期 / 时间",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "event_date"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "OCT-LOFT, Shenzhen",
      "description": "场地 / 地点",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "venue"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Where ideas meet matter",
      "description": "一句话副标题（不需要就填 —）",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "tagline"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "—",
      "description": "必须出现的元素（logo / 嘉宾名 / 主办方 / 赞助商等，不需要就填 —）",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "must_include"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "Professional",
        "Creative",
        "Academic",
        "Family",
        "Youth Culture",
        "Luxury",
        "Casual"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "Professional",
      "description": "受众基调",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "audience"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "Modern Minimal",
        "Bold Editorial",
        "Warm Human",
        "Tech Futurism",
        "Vintage Elegant",
        "Playful Energetic",
        "Serene Premium"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "Modern Minimal",
      "description": "视觉氛围",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "visual_mood"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "Black + Off-White + One Accent",
        "Cream + Earth Tones",
        "Navy + Gold",
        "Bright Multicolor",
        "Pastel Wash",
        "Monochrome Brand Color"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "Black + Off-White + One Accent",
      "description": "配色方向",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "color_palette"
    }
  ],
